sessions.title: HSI Pediatric First Aid | CPR AED  Blended Online + In-Person Skills  Fulfills the CPR/First Aid component of NC DCDEE (10A NCAC 09 .1102); additional NC trainings required for full compliance  Fulfills the CPR/First Aid requirement in CT OEC (Sec. 19a-79-4a); center policies/modules may apply

sessions.section: CPR / AED & First Aid First Aid CPR AED trains anyone with little or no medical training to provide first aid, CPR, and use an automated external defibrillator (AED) in a safe, timely, and effective manner.
